# Workflow layer (Service)

## Read first

- `internal/workflow/booking/workflow.go` ‚Äî state machine, timer, updates
- `internal/workflow/booking/payment.go` ‚Äî validation simulation
- `internal/workflow/booking/activities.go` ‚Äî repository side effects
- [docs/design_overview.md](../../docs/design_overview.md) ¬ß3

## Boundaries

- No Gin/HTTP imports in this package.
- One `BookingWorkflow` per order; workflow ID equals `order_id`.
- Seat mutations only via activities ‚Üí `SeatRepository` (`TryHold`, `Release`, `Confirm`, `SwapHold`).
- Payment uses workflow **updates** (`UpdateSubmitPayment`, `UpdateStartNewPaymentMethod`), not signal polling.
- Timer starts on order create; **refreshes** on every seat change (S-2); **never pauses** during payment (S-4).
- Enforce 3 attempts per code and 3 methods per order in workflow state (S-3).

